Summary: a ball of bright white light
divs: Sighting DetailsI saw a bright white ball of light throbbing or pulsating. and then it zoomed off real fast. woosh!!!!!!!! I have been bothered by it all day and have searched the ne,t watched the news, and checked the newspaper to see if anyone else saw it. What is going on? I am still excited and want to know has there been anyone else out there that has seen it.
